title: Red Rush for CM9 Theme Chooser
creator: Jdcmusicman

extendedInfo.description: The name says is all ...IMPORTANT!!  You MUST be ROOTED and running a ROM that has the CM9 Theme Chooser..THIS has only been tested on a Droid X running Gummy 1.2 and on a Razr Maxx running Cm9It May or May Not work good for other roms..INSTRUCTIONS: Download , Install Go to settings/themes,Select the System Theme , Reboot ,go to settings/themes,Select Red Rush ,click apply *NOTE: If you recieve a message saying " Sorry, this theme is missing assets for your device's screen size"Click  Apply Anyway and REBOOT...There are some things that cannot be themed in Theme Chooser , those things will remain unchanged..*This is a work in progress ,Everything may not be perfect, I may have overlooked some things Although I have tried to make sure I have everything right ..I welcome any Negative or Postive critisim..But remember this theme is FREE and there is plenty of hours involved in making it If you Like my work ,Support it by buying My matching Red Rush Apex or Red Rush Go Launcher Themes from the Playstore(these will be ready soon)So What's Themed ?Framework SystemUISettings ContactsDialer CalculatorCameraEmail (somewhat)GmailSwype betaFacebookGoogle PlaystoreMmsStock KeyboardDropbox Root Explorer (somewhat)Apex (settings icons only) ( I have a matching Apex Theme) Just a few Icons  (I have a matching Apex and Go Launcher theme that will be ready sometime this week)What's going  to be themed next?   if  possible Music Calender and maybe more ....Look forward to Purple Rush and Lime Rush very soon and a very possible  Rainbow Rush (going to try anyway)Special Thanks:Stryker (for some testing and input) Get his themes for Go Launcher and Apex , this man does great work.and whoever else I may have ask questions Google search engine , with out it I would have never learned any of this LOL Thanks to the Gummy Team for their Great Rom Thanks to ALL of the Developers  that make our Smart phones even Smarter :)
